    "steam_appid": 3058740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Odds Chronicles</i> is a tactical roguelite RPG where dice-driven unpredictability meets precise strategy. Play as Evryn, a former royal bodyguard whose kingdom has fallen, and unlock more unique heroes during your journey, each with their own starting abilities and personalized dice loadouts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/25d493857f2ac01c947125ff48b02922.poster.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1170 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/25d493857f2ac01c947125ff48b02922.webm?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/25d493857f2ac01c947125ff48b02922.mp4?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to roll or throw the dice yourself, then use every face like a weapon. Generate resources -<strong>Strength</strong>, <strong>Dexterity</strong> and <strong>Arcane</strong>- to fuel abilities. Charge powerful skills over time or unleash them immediately. Unused resources fill a bonus gauge, granting <strong>Wild Dice</strong> that can shift the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/e3baa0e6f060ec9bd9d01b3ea50576ac.poster.avif?t=1771705085\" width=780 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/e3baa0e6f060ec9bd9d01b3ea50576ac.webm?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/e3baa0e6f060ec9bd9d01b3ea50576ac.mp4?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle on diorama-style battlefields where positioning, line of sight, and ability synergy matter. Assign dice to abilities, adapt to unpredictable rolls, and chain creative combos to turn the tide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/c11a9790ad92ae5d886bf39f2ea6a778.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you go, the deadlier it gets. Upgrade and swap abilities during your run to adapt on the fly. Experiment with new combos, uncover synergies, and build a playstyle that fits how you fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>dice enhancements</strong>, <strong>abilities</strong>, <strong>consumables</strong>, and <strong>relics</strong> to craft a strategy that’s entirely your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/7285403c5a8a2613c9f70895a3987eb7.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=311 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/4b3873cd33a2a81286f269f7b6ae25cf.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=409 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/89fa0fe52022a7ddcc7ecf43f084131d.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run draws from <strong>memories</strong>, yours and others’.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover shifting paths, altered events, and familiar faces in circumstances changed by your past choices. The world of <strong>Lynn</strong> changes as you do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle events your way: with stealth, magic, or brute force, the choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/3e5411070ccb209cb45d66f0e8b91e6f.poster.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1170 height=594 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/3e5411070ccb209cb45d66f0e8b91e6f.webm?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/3e5411070ccb209cb45d66f0e8b91e6f.mp4?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/212b159cba7f85e99c32825fa449b3e4.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each journey, powerful enemies await, tied to the fate of the world itself. Defeat them to reshape the future. Win or lose, you return to the <strong>Tavern outside of Time</strong> with earned <strong>Memory Shards</strong> to gain permanent new powers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/0257f58ef26f8f166854d1eeb8e80c5a.avif?t=1771705085\" width=983 height=1000 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/f542a5a053bcd266a96a89c5d20d9537.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit unique characters bringing new features and upgrades in the <strong>Tavern</strong>. Your first ally, <strong>Kau’i</strong> the blacksmith, will join you with his forge and help you shape new builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between journeys, spend <strong>Memory Shards</strong> to unlock new <strong>skills</strong>, <strong>consumables</strong>, and <strong>talent trees</strong>. Hone your playstyle or experiment new ways to play and prepare for what’s to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/a48ca79a410ea0b26b0d56ac2433f537.poster.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/a48ca79a410ea0b26b0d56ac2433f537.webm?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/a48ca79a410ea0b26b0d56ac2433f537.mp4?t=1771705085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/4b760a228421c61ec077304bd5cadc29.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>As a royal bodyguard, you failed your King, and lost your honor. A tyrant now rules, her lieutenants crushing the realm. You returned too late... but revenge still burns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your revenge against the tyrant ended in defeat. But instead of dying, you awaken in the <i>Tavern Outside of Time</i>, a a mysterious place forged from memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your first mission: return to <strong>Karab’s Peninsula</strong>, where you once fell. The land has changed, but your enemies remain. To reclaim the kingdom of Lynn and restore your legacy, you must fight through ever-shifting regions and confront the truth behind your revenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The revenge you seek is only the beginning. The Tavern holds deeper secrets, and so does your fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/665e20adef95c50e90c9908b9aa4c218.avif?t=1771705085\" width=1600 height=116 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras/a9b88219461d94444bfedc40a6f7a280.avif?t=1771705085\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058740/extras_big/a9b88219461d94444bfedc40a6f7a280.avif?t=1771705085 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A branching adventure with choices on the path and in encounters, plus evolving story events at key Points of Interest,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grid-based tactical combat with terrain elevation, and line-of-sight depth,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Persistent meta-progression with XP, upgrades, and unlockable abilities,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replayable roguelite structure with evolving challenges,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric, tabletop-inspired visuals that bring the world to life,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic relics and consumables ( potions, flasks, and scrolls) to turn the tide in battle,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple playable heroes, each with unique dice pools, abilities, and playstyles</p></li></ul>",
